text: Warrenton, Virginia is a town in the U.S. state of Virginia. The population was 10,057 at the 2020 census, Warrenton is the county seat of Fauquier County. ==References== ==Other websites== * Town of Warrenton official website Category:Towns in Virginia Category:County seats in Virginia Category:1810 establishments in the United States Category:1810s establishments in Virginia
